quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,119,"Refti pellel, Joomi maa, wonannde Й“en huuwirЙ“e bone on majjere, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—um Й“e moЖҙЖҙini, pellet Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  16,120,"Pellet, Ibraahiima woniino Й—owro hoykinaniiЙ—o Alla, ooГұiiЙ—o [e Й—iya diinaaji], o wonaali jeyaaЙ—o e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,121,"YettaynooЙ—o nemaaji Makko Й—in. [Alla] suЙ“ike mo, O fewni mo e laawol focciingol"
  16,122,"Men okki mo ka aduna moЖҙЖҙere. Kanko on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  16,123,"Refi Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, wonnde: \" Jokku diina Ibraahiima ka naayaaki e diinaaji mehre o jeyanooka e sirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  16,124,"Anndee [mawningol fii] aseweere nden ko waЙ—anaa, ko Й“en luutondirЙ“e e mayre. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Гұaawoyoowo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo fii mun"
  16,125,"Noddir e diina Joomi maa kan ГұeeГұal e waaju moЖҙЖҙu. Wennjiraa Й“e e noone Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko Й“uri anndude on majjuЙ—o e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi Й“uri anndi feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  16,126,"Si on yagginay, haray yagginiree yeru no waЙ—iranoЙ—on non. Ko si on muГұГұike, pellet ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  16,127,MuГұГұo! MuГұal maa ngal ko sabu Alla tan. Wata a suno fii maЙ“Й“e. Wata wonu Й“ittorЙ—o e kon ko Й“e fewjata
  16,128,"Pellet, Alla no wonndi e Й“en huluЙ“e [Mo] e Й“en moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e"
